{
  "stem": "13079.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Many of them died as a result of the beatings that they received.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she would report these prisoners for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She also was interested in the lamp shades that were made out of human skin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A prisoner would have a big Spanish galleon on his chest tattooed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well if Ilse saw it, she'd take down his number and he would end up down in the hospital and they'd kill him and skin him and treat the skin and make it into gloves, book ends, different articles including lamp shades.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, she denied all of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we had a witness who was-- had sat as one of her house boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Her husband was a good friend of Himmler's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he had moved around from the different camps and was familiar with all of them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think he was an inspector in some of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, while he was at Buchenwald, Koch mistreated some prisoners who were friends of Josias, Prince of Waldeck, who was the highest ranking SS man in Turania.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] when Koch had permitted these friends of Waldeck's to be beaten and tortured and some of them died, Waldeck got the SS to investigate Koch, Ilse's husband who was a commandant at that time.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the SS court found him guilty of not complying with the concentration camp rules.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was sentenced to be hanged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, Himmler interceded with Hitler and that was commuted and he came back as commandant of-- continued as commandant of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well Waldeck didn't like that a bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And Weldeck being pretty high ranking got a hold of this Colonel Morgan who was a Standartenfuhrer in the SS, and they investigated the financial affairs of Koch while commandant at Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
